text:
Tyler Henry doesn't think Ryan Lochte was swimming alone.

In this sneak peek of this week's episode of Hollywood Medium With Tyler Henry, the TV medium tells Lochte that he senses the 32-year-old Olympian's late grandfather may have been watching over him during the 2016 Olympics in Rio de JaneIro, Brazil.

Lochte looks on in astonishment as Henry describes what he feels,

WATCH: Ryan Lochte Cleared of Criminal Charges in Rio Olympic Robbery Scandal



Watch the clip below for more.

Hollywood Medium With Tyler Henry airs Wednesdays at 9 p.m. ET/PT on E!

EXCLUSIVE: Unlike Michael Phelps, Ryan Lochte Will Not Be Swimming With Sharks for Nat Geo WILD's SharkFest



Meanwhile, the criminal charges against Lochte from his Rio robbery scandal have been dropped.
